OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782485286
OL,3,CSix jailed for murder of woman who was
OL,4,Cinnocent victim of drug war
OL,6,FSix people have been sentenced to life
OL,7,Fin prison for the murder of an
OL,8,Finnocent woman who was shot dead in
OL,9,FMarch 2025, when a turf war between
OL,10,Frival gangs turned violent.
OL,12,FJoanne Penney, 40, died from a single
OL,13,Fgunshot wound to the chest after she
OL,14,Fopened the door of a flat she was
OL,15,Fvisiting in Talbot Green in Rhondda
OL,16,FCyon Taf.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
