OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782485286
OL,3,CSix jailed for murder of woman who was
OL,4,Cinnocent victim of drug war
OL,6,FGunman Huntley was jailed for a
OL,7,Fminimum of 30 years and 146 days,
OL,8,Fwhile 39-year-old co-defendant Renaldo
OL,9,FBaptiste ` who helped orchestrate the
OL,10,Fhit from behind bars ` was jailed for
OL,11,Fa minimum of 42 years for his second
OL,12,Fmurder conviction.
OL,14,FOther gang members were also handed
OL,15,Flife sentences by Mr Justice Fordham
OL,16,Fat Cardiff Crown Court.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
