PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782485286
OL,3,CSix jailed for murder of woman who was
OL,4,Cinnocent victim of drug war
OL,6,FJordan Mills-Smith, 34, was jailed for
OL,7,Fat least 27 years, Joshua Gordon, 28,
OL,8,Fwas given a minimum of 32 years, while
OL,9,FMelissa Quailey-Dashper, 40, will
OL,10,Fspend at least 14 years behind bars
OL,11,Fand Kistina Ginova, 22, will serve at
OL,12,Fleast 12 years.
OL,14,FThe trial previously heard that the
OL,15,Fmotive for the shooting was a clash
OL,16,Fbetween two rival drug gangs operating
OL,17,Fin Talbot Green, Rhondda Cynon Taf.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
