PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782485286
OL,3,CSix jailed for murder of woman who was
OL,4,Cinnocent victim of drug war
OL,6,FSentencing them, Mr Justice Fordham
OL,7,Fsaid: "Joanne Penney was an innocent
OL,8,Fvictim in a drug war. She was 40 years
OL,9,Fold.
OL,11,F"All she did was open a front door at
OL,12,Fa friend's house. No period of
OL,13,Fimprisonment can reflect the value of
OL,14,Fthe life that was taken away by
OL,15,Fmurdering her."
OL,17,FThe judge described how members of Ms
OL,18,FPenney's family had given victim
OL,19,Fpersonal statements to the court,
OL,20,Fdescribing the impact of her death.
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUwD@OO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
