OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782485286
OL,3,CSix jailed for murder of woman who was
OL,4,Cinnocent victim of drug war
OL,6,F"A future taken away, an entire family
OL,7,Fshot through the heart when Joanne
OL,8,FPenney, the mother, daughter and
OL,9,Fsister, loved by so many family and
OL,10,Ffriends was so senselessly taken," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FFive other defendants, Sai Raj Manne,
OL,14,F26, Molly Cooper, 33, Callum Kelleher,
OL,15,F37, Laura John, 23, and Donna James,
OL,16,F51, are to be sentenced later for
OL,17,Foffences connected with the murder.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]
