PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782485286
OL,3,CSix jailed for murder of woman who was
OL,4,Cinnocent victim of drug war
OL,6,FSpeaking after the case, Detective
OL,7,FChief Inspector Lianne Rees, of South
OL,8,FWales Police, said it laid bare "the
OL,9,Fdevastating consequences of organised
OL,10,Fcrime".
OL,12,F"Those responsible showed a complete
OL,13,Fdisregard for human life and for the
OL,14,Fsafety of our communities," she added.
OL,16,F"Let this sentence serve as a stark
OL,17,Fwarning ` if you bring violence, drugs
OL,18,Fand firearms into South Wales, we will
OL,19,Frelentlessly pursue you, dismantle
OL,20,Fyour networks, and ensure you face the
OL,21,Ffull consequences of your actions."
OL,26,@pD@aOUrD@FO]tD@AOUvD@[O]xD@AOU}D@cO]
